
ica.php - the Interactive Clue Aligner


first attempt to create a simple PHP script for alignment visualization
and interactive word alignment
- create some clues and make them accessible to the PHP script
- change settings in config.inc to point to your corpus files 
  and clue databases
- run the script in the browser


tooltip code: taken from
http://www.walterzorn.com/tooltip/tooltip_e.htm

